import { Box, Button, Header, Heading, Text, Tab, Tabs } from 'grommet';
import { Hpe, Previous } from 'grommet-icons';
import React from 'react';



function TabsForm2() {

    return(
        <>
        <Header background="brand">
            <Box direction="row" gap="small" pad="medium">
                <Hpe color="White"/>
                <Text weight="bold">HPE</Text>
                <Text>Console</Text>
            </Box>
        </Header>

        <Box alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'medium' }} >
            <Box pad="small">
            <Button icon={<Previous />} alignSelf="start" primary label="Back" focusIndicator="false"/>
            </Box>
            <Heading margin={{left: 'medium'}} >Asset Tracker</Heading>

            {/* <Box direction="row" alignSelf="start" gap="small">
                <Button primary label="ClickMe" href="/Component/TabsFoem2" size="small"/>
            </Box> */}
            
            <Box direction="row" alignSelf="center"  pad="medium">
           
                <Tabs>
                    <Tab title="Inward Section - Store Activity">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 1</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Shipment & User Details">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 2</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Shipment Delivery Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 3</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Hardware Tagging">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 4</Box>
                    </Tab>
                </Tabs>
            </Box>
        </Box>
        </>
    );
}

export default TabsForm2;
